!pragma layout smetana
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam nodesep 80
skinparam ranksep 80
title CLS-03 - Profili, permessi e decisioni
skinparam shadowing false
hide empty members

class Profile {
  +level : int
  +groups : frozenset[GroupId]
  +version : int?
  +anonymous() : Profile
}

class GroupId <<ValueObject>>
class Level <<ValueObject>> {
  +value : int >= 0
}

class Permission <<Enum>> {
  ALLOW
  DENY
}

class Decision <<Enum>> {
  ALLOWED
  DENIED
}

class JoinOp <<Enum>> {
  AND
  OR
}

class DecisionTrace {
  +subject : SubjectRef
  +profile : Profile
  +operation : OperationName
  +resource : ResourceRef
  +decision : Decision
  +reason : str
  +explicit_deny : bool
  +matched_entry_ids : list[ACLEntryId]
  +visited_resources : list[ResourceRef]
}

class EvaluationResult <<Internal>> {
  +decision : Decision
  +explicit_deny : bool
}

Profile o-- Level
Profile "1" o-- "*" GroupId
Permission --> Decision : contribuisce
JoinOp --> Decision : combina criteri
DecisionTrace --> Decision
DecisionTrace --> EvaluationResult : registra
EvaluationResult --> Decision

note bottom of Profile
  Ogni profilo include sempre il gruppo public.
  L'anonimo usa ANON_SENTINEL, il livello meno privilegiato.
end note

legend
  Vedi anche: [[../attivit%C3%A0/10_risoluzione_profilo.puml ACT-10]] |
  [[../oggetti/08_profilo_anonimo.puml Oggetto anonimo]]
endlegend
@enduml
